  "title": "Three UFOs filmed moving at random [2013]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/03/696/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-be",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>OCT 6th, 2013</strong>. Around 1:44 am in the city of Santo Antônio da Patrulha, State of Rio Grande do Sul, a journalist spotted and <strong>recorded on video</strong> [<span style=\"color:#99ccff;\">see below</span>] three white round UFO’s, apparently small in size and varying the speed as they moved at random, &#8220;crossing and grouping in a single focus&#8221;. The UFO&#8217;s were about 200 meters high and above a high ground, and at a distance of approximately 1,200 meters from the eyewitness. The report of COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command] also informs that the sighting took place in conditions of visibility somewhat impaired by the existing fog at the time and place of the event. The video recording [in 2 parts] with a total duration of 7m31s was attached to the report and made available to the public.</p>\n<h5 style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"color:#99ccff;\"><strong>Videos:</strong></span></h5>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QoA8CkQr5GU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vo_teqFFMjg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.712. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado (ovni) em Santo Antônio da Patrulha, Rio Grande do Sul&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n",
